    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一款“修复反而制造迷宫”的解谜游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Olaf and the Crowning Hangover</strong> 是一款喜剧解谜冒险游戏，你需要拼凑出断片之夜的记忆碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演矮人珠宝商奥拉夫，他在剧烈的头痛中醒来，发现皇家王冠不见了，而刽子手正等着在日出时行刑。为了保住小命，奥拉夫必须重走遍布整个王国的狂欢之路——从被砸烂的酒馆到戒备森严的城堡——并收拾他造成的烂摊子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但有个问题：<strong>恢复秩序会限制你的自由。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/8e21e5534691b6dce1e9c9e6ab1bbcd9.poster.avif?t=1770125569\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/8e21e5534691b6dce1e9c9e6ab1bbcd9.webm?t=1770125569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/8e21e5534691b6dce1e9c9e6ab1bbcd9.mp4?t=1770125569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法反转</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉推箱子开路吧。在这里，你需要通过<strong>拉动</strong>来让世界复原。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>修复即阻碍：</i></strong><i> 你修复的每一把椅子、每一张桌子或每一个桶都会变成坚实的障碍物。</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逆向逻辑：</strong> 你不是在清理空间，而是在消耗空间。你必须仔细规划路线，因为修复房间可能会把你困在死角。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>是拉不是推：</strong> 将重物拖回原位，这种空间谜题彻底颠覆了经典的“推箱子”公式。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/016d54158d62d8d076629896e2ee42d5.poster.avif?t=1770125569\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/016d54158d62d8d076629896e2ee42d5.webm?t=1770125569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/016d54158d62d8d076629896e2ee42d5.mp4?t=1770125569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不仅仅是打扫卫生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奥拉夫的旅程充满了家具之外的危险。为了从这场宿醉中幸存，你需要掌握多种机制：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>“康加舞长队”：</i></strong><i> 召集迷路的顾客并将他们带到安全地带。他们会像<strong>贪吃蛇</strong>一样排队跟着你——小心移动，别被自己的尾巴困住！</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜行与滑行：</strong> 在洒满啤酒的地板上失控滑行，并潜行避开那些不欣赏你手艺的巡逻守卫。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/7a439ae5995f25cb5565894aed9cdcb6.poster.avif?t=1770125569\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/7a439ae5995f25cb5565894aed9cdcb6.webm?t=1770125569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001110/extras/7a439ae5995f25cb5565894aed9cdcb6.mp4?t=1770125569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >至死方休的宿醉</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >起初只是小酌一杯，结果演变成了全国性的灾难。通过<strong>近1000句诙谐的对话</strong>和荒诞的情境解开谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会遇到（并且很可能会惹恼）一群古怪的角色，从脾气暴躁的兽人木匠格里姆拉克，到极力掩饰自己赌博嗜好的查理国王。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>自我阻碍的玩法：</i></strong><i> 独特的寻路机制，你的进度会制造新的障碍。</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样的场景：</strong> 探索酒馆之外的地方——造访锯木厂、城堡和地牢以寻找王冠。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>剧情驱动的战役：</i></strong><i> 充满幽默的叙事，高风险的赌注和色彩丰富的角色阵容。</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古魅力：</strong> 充满活力的像素艺术，融合了怀旧美学与现代解谜设计。</p></li></ul>",
